Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:18.21,Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I got called over by my crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:22.22,Ep_Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,889)}Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:26.90,Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:31.22,Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:43.24,Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's been ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:45.34,Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Have you still not worked up the courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:47.53,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:48.41,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:52.93,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you have a crush on \Nanyone or anything, Takase?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:56.22,Italics,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,What's the correct answer in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:58.54,Italics,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,Should I just say, "you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:02.21,Italics,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,But then I'd be stealing her confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:03.92,Italics,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like I {\i1}don't{\i0} have a crush...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:05.17,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:08.29,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:10.10,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,What? You aren't making sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.64,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Just say so if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:13.78,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine, then, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:15.69,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Fine, then"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:17.53,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,I mean I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:18.81,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:22.39,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't there something you \Nwanted to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:27.18,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like I said, I wanted to know \Nif you had a crush on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.49,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:29.53,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.04,sign_3627_27_Fshh,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(360,1)}Fshh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:33.37,sign_3657_28_Fshhh,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(569,300)}Fshhh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:34.00,sign_3657_28_Fshhh,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(413,1)}Fshh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:38.13,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done? I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:41.08,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.24,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,But I kind of missed my chance today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.90,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm leaving, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:50.15,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.00,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.53,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,W-Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.78,Italics,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,All right, bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.27,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Would you meet up with me tomorrow, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:11.96,Italics,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.87,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll tell you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:15.33,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.87,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,But first, there's something I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:22.07,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.52,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You'll meet up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.79,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:31.97,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot what I was going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:33.40,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.35,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:42.87,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:46.11,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll tell you tomorrow that I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.23,Main,Takase,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:03.27,Italics,Green,0000,0000,0000,,Minagawa-san, the class rep, \Ndoesn't do her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:06.80,sign_5810_53_She_s_a_slacker_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(984,1)}She's a slacker
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:09.75,Main,Green,0000,0000,0000,,Could you help me out a \Nlittle, Minagawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:12.26,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm too lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:14.52,Main,Green,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you become the class rep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.84,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Because I like you, Furuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:20.97,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please not mess with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.36,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.71,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:28.36,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't my intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.38,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not angry, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.43,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I like you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.87,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to be a confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:40.93,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.12,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:46.95,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,But there are rumors that you \Nhang out with lots of guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.81,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a virgin, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:54.45,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I have guy friends, \Nbut it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:55.44,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.78,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:58.26,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:01.84,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd sleep with anyone, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.28,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:06.58,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting horny just \Nimagining me having sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:07.49,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:09.88,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, you're just toying with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.41,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.93,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,But these things are always really awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:16.41,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't tell \Nif you're serious or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:20.25,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you give me an answer \Nif I told you properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.53,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,A-Answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:25.55,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know you that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.64,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.44,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,You could get with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:30.04,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.77,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:40.00,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know anything about dating yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.79,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.99,sign_8228_90_Teehee,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(359,1)}Teehee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.74,sign_8273_91_Shudder,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(148,1)}Shudder
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.49,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,What are you grinning about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.00,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're too adorable, Furuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.83,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,No more, we're done talking about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:55.22,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't given me an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:58.04,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to laugh at me again \Nif I try to answer, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:58.80,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.01,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:05.29,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, specifically how flippant you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.09,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,So reject me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.62,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, can we not talk about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.64,Main,Minagawa,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't {\i1}totally{\i0} hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.28,Main,Furuya,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:23.42,Italics,Blonde,0000,0000,0000,,The student council president saw me smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:26.07,Italics,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.86,sign_9249_107_The_Student_Pres,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Student President's Woes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.54,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good, Kaji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.86,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Akagi! You aren't going \Nto rat me out, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.01,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I'm not a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.77,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you off the hook just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.93,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.73,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,If you give me a kiss, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.47,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you messing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.45,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:48.21,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that's \Nbeen on my mind, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.25,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been in love with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:53.10,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, gay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:54.89,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I tested that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:56.90,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Tested what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.46,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,I just have a hard time \Nfinding interest in women.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.47,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,I can't figure out what's \Nso fun about dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:03.48,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to kiss someone to find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:06.09,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, that sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:08.77,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you how to kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.23,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,No, I know how to kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.40,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.68,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprisingly cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:18.24,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like this is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:21.00,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kiss anyone for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.19,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.08,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,Then how much would you sell your body for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.69,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Say, 100,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:28.65,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:29.46,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:31.08,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.11,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.71,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.22,sign_10879_139_Shudder,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shudder
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.22,sign_10879_140_Shudder,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shudder
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.35,sign_10921_141_Zzzzzip,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(68,1)}Zzzzzip
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:43.58,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,You've never actually prostituted \Nyourself, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:44.22,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.18,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:48.57,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,No one asks for 100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.55,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,That proves you've never \Nactually sold yourself before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.73,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,But 100,000 is actually too little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:57.32,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to value yourself more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.58,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Akagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:01.40,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still asking for that kiss, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.41,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,You are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:03.57,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:05.38,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget our agreement \Nabout your smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.21,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:10.92,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.79,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,All right, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:19.31,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,You reek of tar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.06,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,You reek, Kaji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.84,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! What'd you expect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.43,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,You should quit smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:25.34,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Bite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.39,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, my boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.61,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:47.96,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can fall in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:52.32,Main,President,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you quit smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:53.81,Main,Kaji,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.72,sign_12833_167_Astronomy_Club,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Astronomy Club
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:59.16,Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yukawa-senpai is a third-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.59,Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's graduating tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.80,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, show me the stars again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.88,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,No way. You're too annoying, Sasahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:06.87,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,You suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.82,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to confess to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:11.27,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,How many hundreds of times has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.36,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Shucks, you got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.24,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.46,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bad habit of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:20.75,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I make a joke of my feelings for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.08,sign_13414_178_Spica,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1)}Spica
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:26.67,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell him how I \Nfeel, for real this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:29.96,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,First, I think it's important \Nto set the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.92,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, it's cold. Is it all \Nright if I huddle up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.00,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, stay out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.32,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Also, is it okay if I push you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:41.00,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.01,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.44,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,This is our last time seeing \Nthe stars from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:46.49,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:49.57,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last time seeing \Nthe stars with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.71,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.36,sign_14174_191_ba_dump,Text,0000,0000,0000,,ba-dump
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.36,sign_14174_192_ba_dump,Text,0000,0000,0000,,ba-dump
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:56.27,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we {\i1}could{\i0} see the stars \Ntogether if we really tried, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:57.15,sign_14227_193_Blush___________,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Blush             Blush
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:57.16,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:00.50,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,Have you learned any of the stars yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:03.22,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,No, well, uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.31,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Spica, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:08.03,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first one I taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:12.17,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never forget a star \Nthat {\i1}you{\i0} taught me, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.87,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,Point out Spica, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:20.33,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,Get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.49,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only member \Nin this club next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.34,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,That's your fault, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:26.28,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,You always look so grouchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.61,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:31.92,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,For love, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.08,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:35.67,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad my juniors love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:44.08,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be glad if I {\i1}really{\i0} liked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:47.79,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.72,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I told him I like him \Nwithout joking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:52.28,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Yukawa-senpai \Nwill appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:55.01,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.26,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with this vibe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.31,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Am I making a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.24,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Did I blow it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:02.18,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:03.78,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sasahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.83,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.46,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I was being serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:09.49,Italics,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,I blew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:11.41,Italics,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell him I like him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:13.56,Italics,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:18.28,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I told Senpai I like him so many times over \Nthe past two years we spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:20.32,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I could never tell him I was serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.99,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai's graduating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:25.71,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never get to tell him I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:28.55,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.56,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.45,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to cry in front of Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:33.63,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to worry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.76,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to make it awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:36.93,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to smile like he did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:40.64,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, don't cry, don't cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:47.47,Italics,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:53.09,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of hearing you say you like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.84,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,You're awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:59.41,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,But that ends tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:04.65,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear it one more time before I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.13,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it, if you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:13.40,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:16.31,Main,Sasahara,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.61,Main,Yukawa,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.36,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: "Spring."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.96,sign_17928_247_Spring,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,1)}Spring
